{"title":"Robe of Night","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Robe_of_Night","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.30](/0.30 \"0.30\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n|   |                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |\n| - | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | A long black robe made of strange glossy material. It shrouds its wearer in darkness, reducing the range of vision. According to legend, it was the gift of Ratri the Goddess of the Night to one of her followers. |\n\n[![Robe of night.png](/images/e/e2/Robe_of_night.png)](/File:Robe_of_night.png) ***the +5 robe of Night***\n\n+5 [robe](/Robe \"Robe\")\n\n+40 [will](/Will \"Will\")  \n[See Invisible](/See_Invisible \"See Invisible\")  \n[Line of sight](/Line_of_sight \"Line of sight\") radius reduced by 25% (final LOS rounded down)\n\n## Desirability\n\nFor most species, the **robe of Night**[\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1) reduces line of sight by 2 tiles (only 1 tile for [Kobolds](/Kobold \"Kobold\")). This is clearly useful for [stabbers](/Stab \"Stab\"), as reduced LOS makes it easier to approach [sleeping](/Sleep \"Sleep\") enemies.\n\nThose who would wear a robe anyways may also want this item, as it has good enchantment and a nice willpower bonus. Whether the LOS reduction helps or hurts depends on the character: a [ranged weapon](/Ranged_weapon \"Ranged weapon\") user will find it less useful than a caster relying on low-range spells like [Stone Arrow](/Stone_Arrow \"Stone Arrow\"). In any case, you may prefer an armour with elemental resistances and/or higher AC.\n\n## History\n\n- Prior to [0.20](/0.20 \"0.20\"), the robe of Night had a +4 enchantment.\n- Prior to [0.19](/0.19 \"0.19\"), the robe of Night granted the ability to turn [invisible](/Invisible \"Invisible\") and had a +50 [stealth](/Stealth \"Stealth\") bonus.\n- Prior to [0.12](/0.12 \"0.12\"), the robe of Night did not grant a passive Darkness effect.\n\n## References\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [art-data.txt:987](https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.30.1/crawl-ref/source/art-data.txt#L987) (0.30.1)\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Robe of Night - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Robe_of_Night\",\"wgTitle\":\"Robe of Night\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":77176,\"wgRevisionId\":77176,\"wgArticleId\":4406,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"0.30 articles\",\"Unrands\",\"Body armour\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Robe_of_Night\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":4406,\"wgRequestId\":\"528f43bd465f97495da708c9\",\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[]});mw.loader.state({\"s